      "anxiety_disorders_symptoms_child_separation_family": "My child doesn't like to be away from his/her family.",
      "anxiety_disorders_symptoms_child_afraid_anxiety_panic_attacks": "My child is afraid of having anxiety (or panic) attacks.",
